tags.caratanya:
__**Cara Bertanya**__
1. Defenisikan permasalahan
_<gw ada masalah nih sama ini>_
2. Lalu (jika ada) sertakan usaha yang sudah kalian kerjakan
_<ini code gw> _
3. Setelah itu beritahu apa yang seharusnya program kalian jalankan, dan beritahu juga apa yang malah program kalian jalankan
_<harusnya dia gini, tapi malah gitu>_
tags.tanya: **Jangan tanyakan _apakah ada yang bisa bantu saya?_ Tapi tanyakan langsung permasalahan kalian. Yang lain akan menjawab secepat dan setepat mungkin tanpa harus anda tanyakan bisa atau tidak**
tags.error:
Kalau ingin bertanya _Kenapa error begini?_
**Akan jauh lebih baik jika kalian sertakan:**
-Error di-line keberapa
-Error name
-Code kalian
-Kalau bisa screenshot/kirim code.

tags.nocode:
It’s hard to answer a programming question without code. In order to help, helpers are going to have to see what the code is. (source: https://idownvotedbecau.se/nocode)
Please share your code! If it's short, wrap it directly into Discord. If it's long, use a third-party service (e.g. Hastebin). If you don't know how to wrap code, type `;tag wrapmini`.
tags.wrapmini:
Surround code with:
\`\`\`language
foo = 42
\`\`\`

This outputs:
```languange
foo = 42
```
Replace "language" in the example with java, cpp, python, etc. There should no space/line between the language and the first backtick (`), not to be confused with a single quote (').
tags.imageofcode:
An image of your code is not helpful. Helpers need the text of the code and images are not an acceptable substitute. (source: http://idownvotedbecau.se/imageofcode)
Please share your code as text! If it's short, wrap it directly in Discord. If it's long, use a third-party service (e.g. Hastebin). If you don't know how to wrap code, type `;tag wrapmini`.
tags.selfbot: Please do not discuss or use selfbots: They are expressly forbidden by Discord's Terms of Service. If we find out you're using a selfbot, we'll remove you from the server. Reference: https://support.discordapp.com/hc/en-us/articles/115002192352-Automated-user-accounts-self-bots-

tags.caratanyaeng:
__**How to ask**__
1. Tell us your problem
_<i have problem with ...>_
2. Then include the code that you are working on _(if you have any)_
```this is my code```
3. Afterwards, tell us what should your program do and what does it run instead
_<I want my program do this but instead it does that>_
